    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "a5fe964f47fd248e94508c6a8c7f31f8",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-08T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "37",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Tournament prep - sleep, hydration, opening review only.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-09T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "b2519df9d5f24d49daea849694e3b952",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-09T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "38",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Blitz training - 3+2 daily on Lichess, avoids rating drift.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-10T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "7b11cf8da5e9b2ef38b7b3136cbffb47",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-10T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "39",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Puzzle training - Chess.com puzzle rush, keep pattern sharp.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-11T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "3cdf53ecbf32534843830cfe34b81553",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-11T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "40",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Middlegame plans - IQP structures, minority attacks.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-12T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "120b6207af104799d57147397ddafaa0",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-12T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "41",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Strategic themes - weak squares, outposts, color complexes.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-13T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "fe567a57895a9bccbf68f4df77143a99",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-13T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "42",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Prophylaxis - Nimzowitsch, restrain first, then blockade.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-14T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "32933f68dd496864a1b277bea19efcec",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-14T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "43",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Two weaknesses principle - Dvoretsky, alternate targets.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-15T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "a160a37851612d8b838eb98524c74e64",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-15T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "44",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "King safety - open files near king are critical.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-16T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "6d5c74f97bb02a99eb146c99aaa2099d",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-16T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "45",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Piece activity over material - trade pieces to activate king.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-17T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "a74922b1ae21695b5486978d23e1ee23",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-17T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "46",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Tempo in endgame - triangulation, zugzwang.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-18T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "de9907ad926ff59dcf9c23e0140c60ec",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-18T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "47",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Fortress construction - narrow king, blockade, no pawn breaks.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-19T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "2b38c4a593350f3d5612be49f16ed10f",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-19T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "48",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Rook activity - passive rooks lose endgames.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-20T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "081ea541dcc2e6cb67c9e70a3ceed584",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-20T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "49",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Pawn breaks - single most important middlegame concept.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-21T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "e766459fb5d6542899bb4121f59b57bd",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-21T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "50",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Central control - classical vs hypermodern approaches.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-22T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "d479d7f062afb2deccaaead77d55a2ac",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-22T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "51",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Development - piece before pawn, never move same piece twice.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-23T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "37641aac74f443e595cba3380cedf01e",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-23T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "52",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Castling - almost always kingside except positional need.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-24T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "1fe186675bf17e4dabc70d2c83715e65",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-24T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "53",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Trade theory - trade when ahead in material or in space.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-25T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "c0d8423e028514852aff5429a70c1b76",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-25T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "54",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Weakness principle - target squares one color, then other.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-26T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "6e42b939edbe63824aab8559ace5d286",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-26T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "55",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Isolated pawn - dynamic potential vs long-term weakness.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-27T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "f205a692e4a95f920ae0f1d41ea0e1cc",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-27T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "56",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Backward pawn - target for attack, blockade square weak.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-28T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "973a8f8a7e3791ab50a89ac15da55229",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-28T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "57",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Passed pawn - most valuable in endgame, push relentlessly.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-29T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "4f199b48a79ac12eba92f2221cf4567f",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-29T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "58",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Doubled pawns - not always bad, can control files.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-30T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "a622d46b1410dda7b96b36ac31df11b9",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-30T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "59",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Fianchetto structures - long diagonal bishop, king safety.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-05-31T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "370249a6851701e0b9207a55109e3b33",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-05-31T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "60",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Space advantage - suffocate opponent, avoid trades.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-06-01T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "c78c0c1f721ea7cf6ae89bd73b443acb",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-06-01T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "61",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Coordination - pieces together, not scattered.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-06-02T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "79acbdf95608fd97a33702baec49f04c",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-06-02T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "62",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Initiative - keep opponent reactive, never let them dictate.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-06-03T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "5a05cf3b1a2ce5c224fdd67df9fa22b6",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-06-03T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "63",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Concrete calculation - candidates method, Kotov's tree.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-06-04T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "0dab3eb222900fb4017685400e3b58b0",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-06-04T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "64",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Positional evaluation - Steinitz elements, weak squares.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-06-05T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "be0fa1465df64c834b59e24641c97124",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-06-05T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "65",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Dynamic factors - development, initiative, king safety.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-06-06T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "d6605f35a0ef1b17391f7769f4be3045",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-06-06T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "66",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Static factors - pawn structure, piece placement, material.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-06-07T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "991cc68165ff2c78aeb95da062688c9f",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-06-07T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "67",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Long-term plans - identify at move 15-20, execute over 20 moves.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-06-08T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "f6d624640a52ed24eb99170eeda3e28d",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-06-08T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "68",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Middle game to endgame transition - trade activity for material.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-06-09T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "d53a3b4eb0dc958800e0bb9f24eea91f",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-06-09T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "69",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Openings for me - Ruy Lopez white, Najdorf black, Nimzo Indian.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-06-10T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "5a756ced7ec64cbc15ee424d3c1e01f7",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-06-10T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "70",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Fall Classic prep - study Kaminski's last 30 games.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": "false",
    "created_time": "2026-06-11T00:00:00+00:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "1868935cdb1bd5a79c6bc6cb45154e20",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-06-11T01:00:00+00:00",
    "order": "71",
    "page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "parent_block_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae18544648f",
    "text": "Spring Open prep - Roman's opening choice as white unpredictable.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  }
]